Implemented a narrow deterministic cue-rule refinement in `compiler_registry` lane, focused on the family-conflict patterns from the TODO bundle.

**Changes**
- Expanded conditional-normative cue phrases in the registry so additional legal variants are treated as first-class conditional cues (`upon … terms and conditions`, `subject to … terms and conditions`): [modal_registry.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000110-20260519_134225/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/modal_registry.py:651).
- Refined scope-signal logic in the spaCy codec:
  - Added temporal token-strength signal (`has_temporal_scope_token`) and wired it into temporal scope detection.
  - Added new deterministic backfill branches for `alethic -> deontic` and `epistemic -> temporal`.
  - Extended temporal competing backfill to account for strong epistemic competition.
  - Kept frame-debias behavior conservative by requiring stronger context when only token-level temporal evidence is present.  
  Code: [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000110-20260519_134225/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:33), [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000110-20260519_134225/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:138), [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000110-20260519_134225/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:1757), [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000110-20260519_134225/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:2358), [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-hardened-4codex-gpu-8h-20260519T091017Z-codex-compiler_registry/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-packet-000110-20260519_134225/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:2512).
